# Raw LLM outputs + per-sample scores from the shipped eval run ARE committed —
# the HF Spaces deploy reads them to render the dashboard without live LLM calls.
# Only the per-run aggregates (timestamped) are ignored; they're regenerated by
# `python -m src.report` and don't belong in git.
runs/summary_*.csv
runs/report_*.md
!runs/.gitkeep
